public class TopologyListenerImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.EObjectImpl
implements TopologyListener

An implementation of the model object ' Topology Listener'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Presentation Topology
  • Node To J3D Object Map
  • Topology
  • Java3d Scene Root
  • Node To Node Presentation Map
